  dialogueLines:
  - "One\u2026 Two\u2026 Three\u2026 Four\u2026 "
  - "Oh- great, just as I thought I\u2019d have a moment of privacy\u2026"
  - Sorry, I got lost in the maze.
  - Why are you practising here and not with the others?
  - "Because this spot is the only place where I\u2019m not being watched."
  - "Kind of the point of privacy\u2026"
  - "Watched? Like, by fans or\u2026someone else?"
  - ...
  - "Listen, I\u2019m trying to get my friend Taika out of here."
  - "They claim to love it here, but in this letter they say that they\u2019re scared
    and need my help!"
  - " I\u2019m doing whatever it takes to get them to come home."
  - "Huh\u2026 You\u2019re a good friend."
  - ...
  - Taika is charmed.
  - Charmed?!
  - 'Yes. '
  - The Ringmaster is a powerful man, a snake in disguise.
  - "He makes sure his \u2018show\u2019 is and stays perfect, no matter the means
    necessary\u2026"
  - "That\u2019s awful!"
  - " Why don\u2019t you come with us? If we all leave together, he\u2019ll have
    no power over you anymore."
  - " Hmm\u2026 You\u2019re right."
  - "I will talk to the others, and we will join you. I don\u2019t want us to live
    in fear anymore."
  - Thank you!
  - Good luck, kid.
